# 📖 Chapter 05 – URL Structure

---

# 🎯 Chapter Objective

Is chapter me hum URL Structure ko detail me samjhenge. Aap seekhenge ki SEO-friendly URL kya hota hai, Google URLs ko kaise read karta hai, ek perfect URL kaise design kiya jata hai aur kaun si common mistakes avoid karni chahiye.

---

# 5.1 What is a URL?

**URL (Uniform Resource Locator)** internet par kisi webpage ka unique address hota hai.

Simple Words:

> **URL = Website ke kisi page ka address.**

Example:

```text
https://www.safeprofire.com/fire-extinguisher-mumbai
```

Is URL ko dekhkar hi Google aur user dono samajh sakte hain ki page kis topic ke baare me hai.

---

# 5.2 Why is URL Structure Important?

Ek clean aur descriptive URL Google aur users dono ke liye helpful hota hai.

### Benefits

* Better SEO
* Easy Crawling
* Better User Experience
* Higher Click-Through Rate (CTR)
* Easy Sharing
* Better Website Organization

---

# 5.3 Parts of a URL

Example:

```text
https://www.safeprofire.com/products/fire-extinguisher-mumbai
```

Breakdown:

```text
https://        → Protocol

www.safeprofire.com → Domain Name

/products/     → Folder

fire-extinguisher-mumbai → Slug
```

---

# 5.4 SEO-Friendly URL

Good URL:

```text
https://www.safeprofire.com/fire-extinguisher-mumbai
```

Bad URL:

```text
https://www.safeprofire.com/page?id=45879
```

Google descriptive URLs ko zyada easily understand karta hai.

---

# 5.5 Characteristics of a Good URL

Ek SEO-friendly URL me ye qualities honi chahiye:

* Short
* Readable
* Meaningful
* Keyword Included
* Lowercase Letters
* Hyphens (-) Instead of Underscores (_)
* No Special Characters
* No Random Numbers

---

# 5.6 URL Best Practices

## 1. Use Primary Keyword

Example:

```text
fire-extinguisher-mumbai
```

---

## 2. Keep URL Short

Good:

```text
example.com/fire-alarm
```

Bad:

```text
example.com/best-fire-alarm-system-installation-company-in-mumbai
```

---

## 3. Use Hyphens

Good:

```text
fire-extinguisher-mumbai
```

Bad:

```text
fire_extinguisher_mumbai
```

---

## 4. Use Lowercase Letters

Good:

```text
fire-extinguisher
```

Bad:

```text
FireExtinguisher
```

---

## 5. Avoid Special Characters

Bad:

```text
page@123
```

Good:

```text
fire-safety-guide
```

---

# 5.7 Static vs Dynamic URLs

## Static URL

```text
example.com/fire-hydrant
```

Advantages:

* SEO Friendly
* Easy to Read
* Better User Experience

---

## Dynamic URL

```text
example.com/product?id=245
```

Disadvantages:

* Difficult to Read
* Less SEO Friendly

---

# 5.8 URL Hierarchy

Google website hierarchy ko URLs se bhi samajhta hai.

Example:

```text
Home

↓

Products

↓

Fire Extinguisher

↓

