---

# 5.16 URL Redirection (301 Redirect)

Agar URL change karna zaruri ho to **301 Redirect** use karo.

Example:

Old URL

```text
example.com/fire
```

↓

New URL

```text
example.com/fire-extinguisher
```

301 Redirect ensure karta hai ki users aur search engines automatically new page par chale jayein aur SEO value preserve ho.

---

# 5.17 Canonical URL

Kabhi-kabhi ek hi content multiple URLs par available hota hai.

Canonical URL Google ko batata hai ki original page kaunsa hai.

Example:

```text
https://www.safeprofire.com/fire-extinguisher
```

Canonical use karne se duplicate content issues kam hote hain.

